snippet.title: SYNTHROME GAMEPLAY FOOTAGE
snippet.description:
Hi everyone
We are excited to share this extended gameplay footage of our upcoming demo (May build)
We rebuilt Synthride from scratch (it's Synthride V3.0 now)
and introducing in this footage, the SynthFlyer, a vessel that helps Synthride on its journey. Hope you all are as excited as we are.
Please stay tuned for further updates and demo.

Thanks for sticking around
Best,
SFS Team
